name: STATE v. David COLLINS et al.

parties: STATE v. David COLLINS et al.

opinions.text:
ORDER
On motion of counsel, John L. Cosentino is appointed to represent defendant James Foreman and Gerard DeCelles is appointed to represent defendant Darryl Amado in the prosecution of their appeal.

attorneys: Dennis J. Roberts II, Atty. Gen., Stephen R. Famiglietti, Spec. Asst. Atty. Gen., for plaintiff.
John L. Cosentino, Gerard McG. DeCelles, Alton W. Wiley, Providence, for defendants.
casebody.head_matter:
STATE v. David COLLINS et al.
No. 80-3-C.A.
Supreme Court of Rhode Island.
March 13, 1980.
Dennis J. Roberts II, Atty. Gen., Stephen R. Famiglietti, Spec. Asst. Atty. Gen., for plaintiff.
John L. Cosentino, Gerard McG. DeCelles, Alton W. Wiley, Providence, for defendants.
